data.description:
Welcome to this good bones, west-facing home located in the vibrant community of Golden, Colorado, offering a large backyard and remarkable potential for customization. This residence is equipped with durable metal siding and relatively new roof shingles, approximately three years old, ensuring a robust exterior.

Must watch really cool video walking tour by the listing agent. This video will get you through the house and you can pin point the floor plan and the condition closely. To watch this video link to the virtual tour or type in the address in YouTube Search engine! Please note, this home is currently without a furnace or air conditioning, and lacks a thermostat, but a cement pad is ready in the crawlspace for future furnace installation. Inside, the house awaits your personal touch; it requires cosmetic updates including flooring, appliances, walls, and the replacement of original windows to truly make it shine.

The spacious one-car attached garage adds convenience, while the existing tankless water heater adds a touch of modern efficiency. The kitchen and most flooring areas are primed for remodeling, offering a blank canvas for those looking to infuse their style.

Priced to reflect its condition, this property represents a unique opportunity for those ready to invest in improvements and capitalize on the desirable location in Golden, Colorado. Bring your vision to life in this home that promises both value and potential. We need only cash offers with authentic proof of funds. No wholesalers, we want only cash offers that don't sell to 3rd parties. Even a buyer that wants to occupy this home would be wonderful, yet they must prove cash available funds. It may come down to no appraisal and completely waive the inspection to get this house? The listing agent expects high interest for this house based on the list price! The lowest level with the bedroom and family room technically is the lower level. The MLS is insisting that I call it the basement.
